Sentencas: Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta (SSC) nanowires with 20-100 nm diameters were prepared by electrospinning.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: Subsequent calcination and fragmentation by ultrasonic vibration rendered short nanofibers with 10-40 nm diameters and tens to hundreds nm lengths.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: Slurry containing SSC nanofibers was screen-printed on CGO (Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95) disks to prepare SSC/CGO/SSC symmetrical cells.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: Similar symmetrical cells were also prepared using SSC powder derived from the glycine-nitrate combustion method for comparison.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: AC impedance measurement of the symmetrical cells under open circuit condition revealed that the electrolyte/nanofiber-electrode interfacial area specific resistances (ASR) were 0.533, 0.187, 0.061, 0.026 and 0.010 Omega cm(2) at 500, 550, 600, 650 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: These values were several to more than ten times smaller than the corresponding values of the powder cathodes.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: The large surface area of the nanofibers provide a large number of reaction sites for oxygen reduction and hence low ASRs.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers

Sentencas: A NiO-CGO/CGO/SSC (nanofiber) single cell was also prepared and tested using humidified H-2 as fuel and air as oxidant, the peak power output at 700 degrees C is 1.09 W cm(-2).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of SOFC cathodes made of SSC nanofibers
